These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, lemonade
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, thai, turkish
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, march, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is in an even position##4
2. the thai is on the left of the indian##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the thai is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage   | lemonade       | 7up     | hot-chocolate    |
| Nationality   | turkish   | thai          | indian   |
| Birthday         | may | december | march |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, almond-milk
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, collecting, video-games
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, light-blue, amber
1. the person who likes amber is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the person who likes amber is in an even position##4
6. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | almond-milk  | sprite  |
| Hobby   | video-games | collecting | chess    |
| Color     | brown      | amber    | light-blue |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, car, roller
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, reggae
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, aristoff, davidoff
1. the game-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the davidoff-smoker is the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| Transport          | jet-ski         | roller     | car   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop       | funk     | reggae |
| Cigar         | davidoff | game | aristoff |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, poppy, orchid
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, blue, light-blue
3 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, snake
1. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the person who likes lilac is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| Flower   | dahlia | orchid  | poppy |
| Color        | light-blue | blue  | lilac |
| Pet        | ferret | goldfish | snake         |

