.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, satire, time-travel
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, baccarat, davidoff
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, october, february
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
2. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | romance  | satire  |
| Cigar   | baccarat  | aristoff | davidoff |
| Birthday           | october  | february    | september    |

