.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, aconite, balloon-flower
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, chess, singing
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, software-developer, bartender
1. the person who growszinnia is between the bartender and the person who's hobby is singing##2
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the software-developer is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Flower    | balloon-flower  | zinnia  | aconite        |
| Hobby       | singing | chess | board-games |
| Job   | dressmaker    | software-developer   | bartender   |

