.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-7::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, mauve, light-blue
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, designer, doctor
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding, tennis
1. the person who likes mauve is between the fisherman and the person who likes light-blue##2
2. the doctor is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
4. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| Color   | yellow | mauve        | light-blue |
| Job           | fisherman   | designer      | doctor     |
| Sport         | tennis | skateboarding | golf    |

