.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: corn, pineapple, potato
House: farmhouse, cottage, victorian
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, scientific, thriller
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating corn##1
2. the person watching animation movies is between the victorian house and the person eating potato##2
3. the cottage house is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person eating potato is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching thriller movies is the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3       |
| Food    | corn   | pineapple | potato       |
| House     | victorian  | farmhouse  | cottage |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | animation  | thriller       |

