.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-9::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, drama, satire
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, polish, thai
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, quad-bike
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the pakistani is in an odd position##4
3. the polish is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
4. the pakistani is on the right of the polish##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is between the person driving the scooter and the person watching drama movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |       3       |
| Movie-Genre         | drama | adventure | satire |
| Nationality   | thai       | polish  | pakistani     |
| Transport           | skateboard     | quad-bike     | scooter          |

