.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, nurse, photographer
City: hamburg, london, edinburgh
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, techno, gospel
1. the nurse is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to london is the person traveling to london##1
3. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
4. the chef is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3    |
| Job           | photographer | chef        | nurse   |
| City   | london | edinburgh | hamburg    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel         | pop      | techno |

