.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-12::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, singing, writing
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, train, bike
3 different pets are kept: turtle, hamster, lizard
1. the person driving the train is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the bike is the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3       |
| Hobby         | singing        | dancing  | writing      |
| Transport           | bike | snowmobile | train |
| Pet   | hamster        | turtle   | lizard  |

