.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-13::.
3 different pets are kept: dog, horse, lizard
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, golf, water-polo
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, reggae, gospel
1. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
3. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Pet    | dog        | horse | lizard     |
| Sport       | basketball | golf          | water-polo |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | gospel          | salsa       |

