4. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
5. the scientist is on the far left or far right##3
6. the art-deco house is on the right of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| House          | cottage | art-deco | futuristic |
| Job           | pilot | teacher   | scientist  |
| Color   | coral | emerald   | chestnut        |

