.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-20::.
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, malaysian, nigerian
City: liverpool, colone, boston
3 different pets are kept: cat, fish, lizard
1. the malaysian is between the mexican and the person traveling to colone##2
2. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to boston is the owner of the fish##1
5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
6. the malaysian is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
7. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Nationality         | nigerian      | malaysian | mexican |
| City   | colone | liverpool      | boston    |
| Pet           | lizard      | cat        | fish       |

 